{"tid":193983,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「係咪因為呢個人，所以我而家仲係一個人？」","createTime":"2017-04-09T16:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T03:00:38.000Z","uid":74421,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c1e83467e03a59bc2cd67b7f5b7b1e4ad22e94","tid":193983,"uid":74421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記唔記得我呢？唔記得可以回下帶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/85973/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/85973/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，話說琴晚有個好朋友係Facebook share左呢條片比我，唔講咁多住，睇左片先。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/StakkFactory/videos/vb.526476884227834/695475697327951/?type=2&amp;theater&amp;notif_t=video_reply&amp;notif_id=1491671749851029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStakkFactory%2Fvideos%2Fvb.526476884227834%2F695475697327951%2F%3Ftype%3D2%26theater%26notif_t%3Dvideo_reply%26notif_id%3D1491671749851029&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6295e7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/StakkFactory/videos/vb.526476884227834/695475697327951/?type=2&amp;theater&amp;notif_t=video_reply&amp;notif_id=1491671749851029</a> <br />\n<br />\n「係咪因為呢個人，所以我而家仲係一個人？」<br />\n<br />\n聽完好似即時再失多次戀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗左全日，究竟呢個前度會係我將來幾十年既人生中佔一個咩嘅位置呢？分左手呢一年幾，其實身邊都唔係完全無邂逅過其他女仔，但就總係因為種種原因唔成事。<br />\n<br />\n但其實可能打從心底裡其實我都唔係好想成事，可能，可能就係因為呢個人？"},{"pid":"4c19b92e830b97536d06e20d5765d8cc1fb80fbe","tid":193983,"uid":74421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f9e474545b1ba028f4b0ab1cbcb045399ea228","tid":193983,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"沒有愛，那有恨"},{"pid":"7777c2cb27957d54ad0c2cd776c888da33bd3feb","tid":193983,"uid":74421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒有愛，那有恨</blockquote><br />\n你好憎前度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d032c432a47d5a8710f02056d9b0795e79904c8f","tid":193983,"uid":49919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"我聽到呢句都諗咗陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  究竟自己放底未"},{"pid":"6effae387b4da93e028b03c2384f1ea56d49d33d","tid":193983,"uid":74421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聽到呢句都諗咗陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  究竟自己放底未</blockquote><br />\n有新一個未先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c83b97dd570bbf29bbde21a41f2227699657a6a","tid":193983,"uid":63449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363ba96dcfb9685aace35cbb53828b35e21b3873","tid":193983,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沒有愛，那有恨</blockquote><br />\n你好憎前度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n的確<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e347483470d4590f02cf7320ac828b93e1f292","tid":193983,"uid":74421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好耐無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb44d02f56f3f3893cb782cf517f970924fe4c